title: EPL - Match of the Day Two 30.09.2018 480p SD
description:
EPL - Match of the Day Two 30.09.2018 480p SD
Highlights and reaction from the day's Premier League fixture between promoted Cardiff City and Burnley, introduced by Jason Mohammad.

Both sides have endured a tough start to the domestic season but Cardiff went into the game on a 13-match unbeaten run in this fixture spanning 11 years.

There's also a round-up of all the goals from Saturday's eight games, including Chelsea v Liverpool
